                "invention-title": [
                    "Novel slurry residue treatment process in methyl chlorosilane monomer synthesis",
                    "一种甲基氯硅烷单体合成中浆渣处理新工艺"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the technical field of methyl chlorosilane production processes, and discloses a novel slurry residue treatment process in methyl chlorosilane monomer synthesis, which comprises the following steps: S1, high-boiling-point substance removal by a flash evaporation system: slurry residues enter the flash evaporation system, and the high-boiling-point substances are evaporated in a heating and pressure reduction manner; s2, pressurized hydrolysis dechlorination: enabling the low-boiling-point residues subjected to flash evaporation treatment to enter a pressurized hydrolysis system, and reacting with water to remove chlorine elements; s3, washing: washing the hydrolysate with water to remove residual hydrogen chloride and other water-soluble impurities; s4, solid-liquid separation: centrifuging and filtering the washed substance, and separating solid and liquid in the washed hydrolysate; s5, performing low-temperature calcination: performing low-temperature calcination on the solid residues to remove residual moisture and organic matters; the process has the advantages that the copper recovery rate is increased, toxic and harmful elements are prevented from being introduced into organic silicon production and manufacturing, and meanwhile environmental pollution is relieved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及甲基氯硅生产工艺技术领域，且公开了一种甲基氯硅烷单体合成中浆渣处理新工艺，包括以下步骤S1、闪蒸系统脱除高沸物：浆渣进入闪蒸系统，通过加热和减压的方式，使得高沸点物质蒸发；S2、加压水解脱氯：经过闪蒸处理后的低沸物残留进入加压水解系统，与水反应脱除氯元素；S3、水洗：水解产物经过水洗，去除残余的氯化氢和其他水溶性杂质；S4、固液分离：对经过水洗的物质通过离心和过滤，将洗净水解产物中的固体和液体进行分离；S5、低温煅烧：固体残渣经过低温煅烧，去除残余的水分和有机物；本发明提高的上述工艺具有提高铜回收率，防止有毒有害元素引入有机硅生产制造，同时减轻对环境污染的优点。"
                }
            ]
